Package fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.identity.impl

Class PairLocalScope

java.lang.Object
fr.cnrs.iees.omugi.identity.impl.PairLocalScope
All Implemented Interfaces:
IdentityScope
public class PairLocalScope extends Object implements IdentityScope

A local scope for an identity based on a pair label+name. Works with PairIdentity. It works basically like LocalScope, except that it uses two Strings to construct its identifiers.

Author:
Jacques Gignoux - 28 janv. 2019
